WEBVTT

1
00:03:20.060 --> 00:03:21.270
This is Bhopal...

2
00:03:21.680 --> 00:03:24.890
I won't bore you with
what's famous here...

3
00:03:25.020 --> 00:03:27.270
That's all on Google anyway.

4
00:03:27.480 --> 00:03:30.310
I'm going to tell you
about a man

5
00:03:30.350 --> 00:03:32.430
Google itself is trying
to figure out...

6
00:03:32.560 --> 00:03:35.610
wondering why the hell
his stars are so cursed...

7
00:03:35.680 --> 00:03:39.180
so cursed that he's always
running from trouble.

8
00:03:55.890 --> 00:03:58.680
This here is my childhood friend.
Mohan Sharma.

9
00:03:59.230 --> 00:04:01.310
Today Mohan's running
"from" marriage...

10
00:04:01.350 --> 00:04:02.760
but there was a time...

11
00:04:02.850 --> 00:04:05.390
when he was running around
"to" get married.

12
00:04:07.100 --> 00:04:08.550
The skies are clear.

13
00:04:08.640 --> 00:04:10.600
both players are clear on
their game plan too.

14
00:04:10.680 --> 00:04:12.930
Both are proceeding
towards their goal.

15
00:04:13.020 --> 00:04:16.690
Nothing can stop them
from winning today.

16
00:04:16.770 --> 00:04:18.860
This pair is going to create history.

17
00:04:18.930 --> 00:04:19.930
Bam!

18
00:04:26.600 --> 00:04:28.140
And this is the love of his life...

19
00:04:28.230 --> 00:04:29.270
Saniya Hussain.

20
00:04:29.680 --> 00:04:31.300
Mohan Sharma and Saniya Hussain...

21
00:04:31.560 --> 00:04:32.730
Get it?

22
00:04:32.810 --> 00:04:34.190
You do. right?

23
00:04:34.390 --> 00:04:36.180
But their families didn't.

24
00:04:36.390 --> 00:04:38.260
Both sides were dead against it...

25
00:04:38.520 --> 00:04:40.270
Neither did his "papa"
approve of it nor did her "abba."

26
00:04:40.640 --> 00:04:43.050
So they went looking
for help from Baba.

27
00:04:44.020 --> 00:04:46.810
Bow your heads before all.
whether it's Kashi or Kaba.

28
00:04:46.890 --> 00:04:50.300
Get solution for every problem
from Engineer Baba!

29
00:04:51.350 --> 00:04:52.100
Shall we?

30
00:04:54.350 --> 00:04:57.010
You sure going
this high up will help?

31
00:04:57.310 --> 00:04:58.810
I've got faith in the One above...

32
00:04:59.810 --> 00:05:01.020
and this one's perched
pretty high too.

33
00:05:17.390 --> 00:05:25.180
<i>In every journey.
I want you near.</i>

34
00:05:25.310 --> 00:05:33.190
<i>Your sight's the only thing
I hold dear.</i>

35
00:05:33.390 --> 00:05:41.260
<i>I want to live where
your heartbeat stays.</i>

36
00:05:41.310 --> 00:05:48.440
<i>In my thoughts forever too.
through endless days.</i>

37
00:05:48.600 --> 00:05:52.470
<i>I wish to steal you
from the world's hold.</i>

38
00:05:52.640 --> 00:05:56.680
<i>I ask God for you and nothing more.</i>

39
00:05:56.770 --> 00:06:04.560
<i>I'll never let you go.</i>

40
00:06:04.640 --> 00:06:12.760
<i>I am in love with you with
all my heart and soul.</i>

41
00:06:12.850 --> 00:06:20.260
<i>I am in love with you with
all my heart and soul.</i>

42
00:06:21.310 --> 00:06:29.230
<i>In every journey.
I want you near.</i>

43
00:06:29.350 --> 00:06:37.260
<i>Your sight's the only thing
I hold dear.</i>

44
00:06:52.810 --> 00:07:00.810
<i>We made a deal.
your heart for mine.</i>

45
00:07:00.890 --> 00:07:08.800
<i>Once you were mine.
I left all behind.</i>

46
00:07:08.890 --> 00:07:12.800
<i>Whether I benefit or lose.</i>

47
00:07:12.890 --> 00:07:20.140
<i>I choose the path my heart would choose.</i>

48
00:07:20.770 --> 00:07:24.610
<i>I care for none. just you.</i>

49
00:07:24.680 --> 00:07:28.550
<i>In your winds. I drift and I lose.</i>

50
00:07:28.640 --> 00:07:36.140
<i>You live in every prayer I behold.</i>

51
00:07:36.640 --> 00:07:44.600
<i>I am in love with you with
all my heart and soul.</i>

52
00:07:44.680 --> 00:07:53.140
<i>I am in love with you with
all my heart and soul.</i>

53
00:07:53.350 --> 00:08:01.300
<i>In every journey.
I want you near.</i>

54
00:08:01.350 --> 00:08:08.510
<i>Your sight's the only thing I hold dear.</i>

55
00:08:10.980 --> 00:08:12.110
Baba! Greetings!

56
00:08:12.180 --> 00:08:13.140
Greetings!

57
00:08:13.680 --> 00:08:14.430
Bless you. son.

58
00:08:14.520 --> 00:08:16.060
Sit down. Be comfortable.

59
00:08:16.140 --> 00:08:16.800
Okay.

60
00:08:16.930 --> 00:08:18.260
What problem do you face. dear?

61
00:08:19.230 --> 00:08:21.060
- Baba. we want to get married.
- Yes. Baba.

62
00:08:21.140 --> 00:08:22.390
Then get married.

63
00:08:22.560 --> 00:08:23.980
Son. get two garlands. please.

64
00:08:24.140 --> 00:08:26.470
Baba. I'm Hindu and she's Muslim.

65
00:08:26.560 --> 00:08:27.480
Don't bother!

66
00:08:28.270 --> 00:08:29.770
Then you'll get beaten up.

67
00:08:29.850 --> 00:08:30.930
and you get me
beaten up too!

68
00:08:31.020 --> 00:08:33.310
Baba. who's going to climb
all these steps to beat you?

69
00:08:33.390 --> 00:08:35.100
Trust me.

70
00:08:35.230 --> 00:08:38.270
people might not climb to donate.

71
00:08:38.430 --> 00:08:40.800
but they'll sprint up
to throw punches for sure.

72
00:08:40.890 --> 00:08:42.760
You know.
I used to sit at a thousand steps

73
00:08:42.890 --> 00:08:44.800
and had to move up to five thousand
just to save my skin?

74
00:08:44.930 --> 00:08:45.890
You are right.

75
00:08:45.980 --> 00:08:49.310
but there's got to be some
solution for sure.

76
00:08:49.560 --> 00:08:50.810
- You've got a thousand...
- Excuse me?

77
00:08:50.890 --> 00:08:52.890
You've got a thousand
problems in this wedding.

78
00:08:52.980 --> 00:08:55.150
You think a hundred
bucks can fix it all?

79
00:08:55.230 --> 00:08:57.270
Baba. just get us married...

80
00:08:57.430 --> 00:09:00.640
I promise.
I'll get your hut rebuilt.

81
00:09:00.730 --> 00:09:03.310
Tell me. will we ever
get married or not?

82
00:09:03.390 --> 00:09:05.390
Not?! Don't even think about not.

83
00:09:05.480 --> 00:09:07.270
We will definitely get married.

84
00:09:07.430 --> 00:09:10.760
Look. if fate doesn't approve.
you'll forget him someday.

85
00:09:10.850 --> 00:09:12.300
That's not possible.

86
00:09:12.350 --> 00:09:13.760
Everything is possible.

87
00:09:14.640 --> 00:09:16.350
Life's just math...

88
00:09:16.730 --> 00:09:18.190
Everything's predetermined.

89
00:09:18.560 --> 00:09:21.060
If I can be an engineer
who turned into a baba.

90
00:09:21.140 --> 00:09:23.300
then you too can forget him.

91
00:09:23.390 --> 00:09:25.760
I'd rather die than forget him.

92
00:09:26.020 --> 00:09:27.730
We will definitely get married...

93
00:09:27.850 --> 00:09:30.600
even if we have to fight
two religions or four!

94
00:09:34.230 --> 00:09:34.900
Let's go.

95
00:09:34.980 --> 00:09:36.940
Baba. do you have a lift here?

96
00:09:37.020 --> 00:09:38.940
Forget the lift to go down. son...

97
00:09:39.100 --> 00:09:40.930
the road you've taken.

98
00:09:41.140 --> 00:09:42.850
someone will soon give you
a lift to heaven.

99
00:09:43.100 --> 00:09:43.890
- Let's get out of here.
- Come on now. Baba!

100
00:09:43.980 --> 00:09:46.150
Please don't say such
inauspicious things!

101
00:09:48.480 --> 00:09:50.110
Just pray it all goes right this time.

102
00:09:50.180 --> 00:09:51.390
I'm already doing that!

103
00:09:51.480 --> 00:09:52.940
I also took you to the Baba yesterday.

104
00:09:53.020 --> 00:09:54.900
but you wouldn't even listen to him.

105
00:09:54.980 --> 00:09:57.270
I don't want to hear a word
against our wedding.

106
00:09:57.310 --> 00:09:59.310
I fell for you when you were 16...

107
00:09:59.390 --> 00:10:01.220
You're 32 now.

108
00:10:01.390 --> 00:10:02.260
So what?

109
00:10:02.520 --> 00:10:03.980
You can still have kids till 65.

110
00:10:04.060 --> 00:10:05.110
I checked.

111
00:10:05.730 --> 00:10:07.190
So you'll marry me
after you turn 65?

112
00:10:07.270 --> 00:10:09.110
No. sweetheart. today...
right now.

113
00:10:09.600 --> 00:10:11.600
By the way.
where are our witnesses?

114
00:10:11.680 --> 00:10:12.930
Hubby's bringing them.
There he is.

115
00:10:18.480 --> 00:10:19.560
And this is me.

116
00:10:20.020 --> 00:10:22.690
his friend. Harbir Singh aka Hubby...

117
00:10:22.890 --> 00:10:26.220
witness to every disaster
and wedding in his life.

118
00:10:26.310 --> 00:10:29.060
Amritsari James Bond.
hurry up or the registrar will leave!

119
00:10:29.140 --> 00:10:30.140
Where are the witnesses?

120
00:10:30.430 --> 00:10:32.140
Come on. guys!

121
00:10:32.270 --> 00:10:33.480
Let's go.

122
00:10:36.270 --> 00:10:37.270
There they are.

123
00:10:38.810 --> 00:10:40.770
Who the hell are these people?

124
00:10:40.850 --> 00:10:43.510
Our friends are tired of being
witnesses to your wedding.

125
00:10:43.600 --> 00:10:46.180
I got these from the crossroads.
after a lot of convincing.

126
00:10:46.310 --> 00:10:48.270
Beggars are going to be
witnesses at our wedding?

127
00:10:48.350 --> 00:10:50.430
What. you want
the prime minister to step in?

128
00:10:50.680 --> 00:10:53.470
Sister-in-law. their blessings
actually work. try to understand.

129
00:10:53.810 --> 00:10:55.020
- Hello. sir.
- Hello. Dada.

130
00:10:55.100 --> 00:10:56.470
Hide that begging
bowl under your vest.

131
00:10:56.560 --> 00:10:57.230
Sure.

132
00:10:57.310 --> 00:10:58.150
Hurry up already.

133
00:11:05.140 --> 00:11:06.720
- Hello.
- Hi.

134
00:11:07.350 --> 00:11:08.930
You two come here every year. son.

135
00:11:09.020 --> 00:11:10.190
Sir. what do we do. our parents--

136
00:11:10.270 --> 00:11:12.690
You've come to court
for marriage more times

137
00:11:12.930 --> 00:11:14.850
than others come for divorce.

138
00:11:14.930 --> 00:11:16.300
Sir. this is the final time...

139
00:11:16.390 --> 00:11:18.470
please get us married today.

140
00:11:18.560 --> 00:11:20.110
Yes sir. if you could
speed it up a bit...

141
00:11:20.180 --> 00:11:21.470
they've got to get back to begging--

142
00:11:21.560 --> 00:11:22.980
They've got work to get back to.

143
00:11:26.230 --> 00:11:27.480
I'm his friend.

144
00:11:27.680 --> 00:11:29.800
They're his relatives...
distant relatives.

145
00:11:30.310 --> 00:11:33.560
Yes. I can tell...
they've come from pretty far out.

146
00:11:34.180 --> 00:11:36.930
I recognize him...
Gandhinagar signal. right?

147
00:11:37.020 --> 00:11:38.270
Yes. sir.

148
00:11:39.980 --> 00:11:41.520
But what's the use?

149
00:11:41.810 --> 00:11:43.270
Before you sign the papers.

150
00:11:43.390 --> 00:11:46.260
your "abba" will walk
through that door.

151
00:11:46.350 --> 00:11:47.430
Stop!

152
00:11:48.390 --> 00:11:51.390
Mr. Registrar.
this wedding can't take place!

153
00:11:51.480 --> 00:11:52.230
- Abba?!
- Quiet!

154
00:11:52.680 --> 00:11:53.390
Come home with me!

155
00:11:53.480 --> 00:11:54.270
No. I won't!

156
00:11:54.310 --> 00:11:56.060
And your father will walk
through that other door.

157
00:11:56.140 --> 00:11:56.800
Mohan!

158
00:11:58.180 --> 00:11:59.100
Father?

159
00:11:59.180 --> 00:12:00.890
I'll break your legs!

160
00:12:01.350 --> 00:12:03.550
How dare you get married
against my wishes?

161
00:12:03.640 --> 00:12:04.550
Come with me right now!

162
00:12:04.640 --> 00:12:06.510
- Father. I love Saniya--
- Shut up!

163
00:12:07.890 --> 00:12:09.760
Mr. Registrar. how could you...

164
00:12:10.310 --> 00:12:13.980
They're fools and you are
the sensible one.

165
00:12:14.060 --> 00:12:15.610
Talk some sense into them.

166
00:12:15.680 --> 00:12:17.600
- Me?
- Yes. you.

167
00:12:17.680 --> 00:12:19.220
What will he say?

168
00:12:19.310 --> 00:12:21.230
I'll tell you who you'll marry!

169
00:12:21.350 --> 00:12:24.680
And I'll show you
who you'll marry!

170
00:12:24.810 --> 00:12:25.730
Get lost!

171
00:12:26.230 --> 00:12:28.730
Father! Father. please listen...

172
00:12:35.430 --> 00:12:36.760
Father. why don't you understand

173
00:12:36.850 --> 00:12:37.640
if I don't marry Saniya--

174
00:12:37.730 --> 00:12:40.310
Don't you dare say
her name again!

175
00:12:40.520 --> 00:12:43.270
I've said 50 times already.
I'll only marry the man I want.

176
00:12:43.310 --> 00:12:46.560
And I've said a 100 times.
you'll marry the man I choose.

177
00:12:46.770 --> 00:12:48.650
Zeenat. talk some sense into her.

178
00:12:48.810 --> 00:12:51.110
At least you should give a
chance to speak. dear...

179
00:12:51.180 --> 00:12:52.640
- Huh?
- I don't want to hear a word.

180
00:12:52.730 --> 00:12:54.150
I'll only marry Mohan.

181
00:12:54.230 --> 00:12:56.400
What? Does government provide
subsidy if you do that?

182
00:12:56.480 --> 00:12:57.520
I don't want to hear a word.

183
00:12:57.600 --> 00:12:58.890
I'll only marry Saniya.

184
00:12:58.980 --> 00:13:00.400
Son. if you really want
to ruin your life.

185
00:13:00.480 --> 00:13:01.940
gamble on cricket.

186
00:13:02.020 --> 00:13:03.730
but don't marry outside your faith.

187
00:13:03.810 --> 00:13:05.190
He's right.

188
00:13:05.270 --> 00:13:06.650
What he says goes.

189
00:13:06.730 --> 00:13:09.020
You'll be getting married to Meera.

190
00:13:09.680 --> 00:13:11.850
You're marrying Mehmood!

191
00:13:11.980 --> 00:13:13.310
Yes. Mehmood.

192
00:13:13.350 --> 00:13:14.350
Ew!

193
00:13:18.020 --> 00:13:19.060
I see.

194
00:13:19.140 --> 00:13:19.890
Where did you get it from?

195
00:13:20.020 --> 00:13:21.520
Nuraani Hotel.

196
00:13:21.600 --> 00:13:23.720
- They made special--
- Mr. Mirza...

197
00:13:29.350 --> 00:13:30.350
You?

198
00:13:30.560 --> 00:13:32.860
You want your daughter
to marry Mehmood. right?

199
00:13:34.270 --> 00:13:36.060
Then I'm ready to become
Mehmood for Saniya.

200
00:13:41.230 --> 00:13:43.480
No. I don't want you
change your faith.

201
00:13:43.560 --> 00:13:44.860
Love isn't about changing someone.

202
00:13:44.930 --> 00:13:46.680
Mr. Mirza... it's about accepting
them as they are.

203
00:13:47.140 --> 00:13:50.300
And I'm willing
to do anything for love.

204
00:13:53.890 --> 00:13:56.600
If he's doing it out of his own will.
then what's the problem?

205
00:13:56.850 --> 00:13:58.140
Saniya's warned us that

206
00:13:58.230 --> 00:14:00.150
if she doesn't get
to marry Mohan.

207
00:14:00.230 --> 00:14:02.020
she'll end her life
on the wedding night.

208
00:14:02.770 --> 00:14:05.520
And when she realizes
the groom is actually Mohan.

209
00:14:05.600 --> 00:14:06.970
she'll go crazy with happiness.

210
00:14:07.060 --> 00:14:08.560
She'll go crazy with happiness. sure.

211
00:14:08.640 --> 00:14:09.930
but what about the real Mehmood.

212
00:14:10.020 --> 00:14:12.360
who'll lose his mind in rage?

213
00:14:12.430 --> 00:14:13.220
Tell him no.

214
00:14:13.270 --> 00:14:14.110
Tell him not to bring the wedding
procession to our place.

215
00:14:14.180 --> 00:14:14.800
You are strange!

216
00:14:14.890 --> 00:14:16.260
You think he's delivering pizza
or what?

217
00:14:16.350 --> 00:14:17.890
He's bringing a wedding procession!
We can't cancel that last minute.

218
00:14:17.980 --> 00:14:19.110
I don't care...

219
00:14:19.560 --> 00:14:21.770
the only thing I care about
is my daughter's life.

220
00:14:24.680 --> 00:14:25.550
Hello...?

221
00:14:26.520 --> 00:14:27.400
Hello...?

222
00:14:29.480 --> 00:14:30.270
Hello...?

223
00:14:30.930 --> 00:14:31.680
Yes. Mr. Mirza?

224
00:14:31.770 --> 00:14:33.270
Mehmood. do one thing.

225
00:14:33.310 --> 00:14:34.270
don't bring the wedding
procession to our place.

226
00:14:34.310 --> 00:14:35.150
Come again?

227
00:14:35.600 --> 00:14:36.970
I shouldn't don't bring the wedding
procession to your place?

228
00:14:38.390 --> 00:14:40.890
What nonsense...
I've already paid for the band!

229
00:14:41.060 --> 00:14:43.060
Don't worry about that.
I'll make Mohan pay for it.

230
00:14:43.140 --> 00:14:44.510
My relatives are already here.

231
00:14:44.680 --> 00:14:46.140
Then send them with Mohan...

232
00:14:46.230 --> 00:14:48.940
he's a new Muslim.
he won't have relatives yet.

233
00:14:49.600 --> 00:14:51.970
You're not taking me seriously!

234
00:14:52.060 --> 00:14:54.690
You're not admitted into a hospital
for me to take you seriously.

235
00:14:54.770 --> 00:14:55.860
Please. forgive me.

236
00:14:55.930 --> 00:14:57.890
I'll find you another girl.

237
00:14:58.020 --> 00:15:00.400
I don't want another girl.
I want to marry Saniya.

238
00:15:00.480 --> 00:15:02.150
If I don't marry her.
God help me. I'll lose it.

239
00:15:02.230 --> 00:15:04.560
Fine. go lose it then. I can't help it.
Do what you please.

240
00:15:08.140 --> 00:15:09.140
- Gaffur...?
- Yes. bro?

241
00:15:09.430 --> 00:15:10.140
Where's the band?

242
00:15:10.310 --> 00:15:11.520
I sent them to Mohan's place.

243
00:15:11.600 --> 00:15:12.470
And the wedding guests?

244
00:15:12.560 --> 00:15:13.400
Sent them too.

245
00:15:13.480 --> 00:15:14.270
And I'm left with what...?

246
00:15:15.180 --> 00:15:15.850
This.

247
00:15:15.930 --> 00:15:17.470
You think your father's getting
married out there?

248
00:15:24.730 --> 00:15:25.980
- Hubby...?
- Yeah?

249
00:15:26.060 --> 00:15:27.730
How'd you manage to gather
so many guests so fast?

250
00:15:27.810 --> 00:15:28.900
You order them off Blinkit?

251
00:15:28.980 --> 00:15:31.060
No bro. in their culture.

252
00:15:31.140 --> 00:15:32.260
whether it's a wedding or a funeral.

253
00:15:32.350 --> 00:15:33.600
people turn up just
to share the sorrow.

254
00:15:33.680 --> 00:15:35.350
You calling my wedding a funeral?

255
00:15:35.430 --> 00:15:36.550
Mark my words. you'll die single.

256
00:15:36.680 --> 00:15:38.300
Don't make the groom
on the horse curse you!

257
00:15:39.180 --> 00:15:40.430
Wonderful! Wonderful!

258
00:15:40.560 --> 00:15:42.560
The groom looks amazing.

259
00:15:42.640 --> 00:15:43.720
Come with me.

260
00:15:43.810 --> 00:15:45.480
Everyone's waiting for the wedding.
Come on. join me.

261
00:15:45.640 --> 00:15:46.970
Hey. your hat...

262
00:15:47.680 --> 00:15:48.390
Yes. let's go.

263
00:15:48.480 --> 00:15:50.060
- You can come however you want.
- I'll fetch him. I'll fetch him.

264
00:15:50.140 --> 00:15:51.640
- Please. get him inside.
- You carry on.

265
00:15:52.600 --> 00:15:56.600
In the name of Allah.
the most merciful. the most gracious...

266
00:15:57.060 --> 00:15:58.190
No. it's Mehmood!

267
00:16:00.230 --> 00:16:02.810
Mr. Mehmood Ali. son of Usman Ali.

268
00:16:02.980 --> 00:16:06.940
you are being married to
Miss Saniya. daughter of Mirza Ali.

269
00:16:07.020 --> 00:16:09.560
with a Mehr of Rs. 10.000.

270
00:16:09.640 --> 00:16:11.470
- Do you accept it?
- I do.

271
00:16:11.560 --> 00:16:13.360
- You do?
- Yes. I do!

272
00:16:13.430 --> 00:16:15.390
- You do?
- Yes. I do. uncle!

273
00:16:15.520 --> 00:16:16.480
He's not deaf.

274
00:16:16.560 --> 00:16:17.650
In our faith.
you've got to say it three times.

275
00:16:17.730 --> 00:16:18.650
Oh. I see!

276
00:16:25.770 --> 00:16:27.400
In the name of Allah. the most merciful.
the most gracious...

277
00:16:27.480 --> 00:16:29.860
Miss Saniya Hussain.
daughter of Mirza Ali.

278
00:16:29.930 --> 00:16:31.850
you are being married to
Mr. Mehmood Ali.

279
00:16:31.930 --> 00:16:36.680
son of Usman Ali.
with a Mehr of Rs. 10.000.

280
00:16:36.930 --> 00:16:38.930
- Do you accept it?
- I do.

281
00:16:39.060 --> 00:16:40.940
- You do?
- I do.

282
00:16:41.020 --> 00:16:42.690
- You do?
- I do.

283
00:16:42.770 --> 00:16:44.270
Congratulations.
I declare you as married.

284
00:16:44.350 --> 00:16:45.720
You may now move
the flower curtains away.

285
00:16:45.890 --> 00:16:47.260
Congratulations! Congratulations!

286
00:16:48.640 --> 00:16:49.930
Congratulations! Congratulations!

287
00:16:50.020 --> 00:16:51.520
You may now see the bride's face.

288
00:16:51.600 --> 00:16:52.300
Thank you.

289
00:16:52.680 --> 00:16:53.680
Thanks.

290
00:16:57.020 --> 00:16:58.520
- Greetings.
- Greetings to you as well.

291
00:17:00.850 --> 00:17:02.260
Congratulations. my love.

292
00:17:02.770 --> 00:17:04.980
The moment we've been
waiting for is finally here.

293
00:17:13.310 --> 00:17:14.480
Who are you?

294
00:17:15.270 --> 00:17:16.400
Where's Saniya?!

295
00:17:16.680 --> 00:17:17.680
Ruhi?!

296
00:17:17.930 --> 00:17:19.100
- You?!
- Ruhi!!!

297
00:17:19.180 --> 00:17:20.300
Where's Saniya?!

298
00:17:23.810 --> 00:17:27.020
Mr. Mehmood.
she didn't want to marry you.

299
00:17:27.430 --> 00:17:29.930
She loves someone
named Mohan.

300
00:17:30.270 --> 00:17:33.650
She ran away and put me
in her place.

301
00:17:33.730 --> 00:17:35.810
I'm your Saniya now.

302
00:17:35.980 --> 00:17:37.270
- This is absurd!
- You...

303
00:17:37.350 --> 00:17:40.850
Mr. Mirza. you didn't tell her
I was coming to marry her?!

304
00:17:40.930 --> 00:17:41.970
I wanted to surprise her.

305
00:17:42.060 --> 00:17:43.520
That's one hell of a surprise!

306
00:17:43.640 --> 00:17:44.800
I'm the one surprised here!

307
00:17:44.980 --> 00:17:45.770
I don't accept this wedding.

308
00:17:45.850 --> 00:17:46.470
But the wedding's already
taken place.

309
00:17:46.560 --> 00:17:47.310
How did it take place?

310
00:17:47.350 --> 00:17:48.260
Say something. man!

311
00:17:48.430 --> 00:17:50.680
Bro. if this was a Gurudwara.
I'd know what to do.

312
00:17:50.810 --> 00:17:52.230
I've got no clue how
this works here.

313
00:17:52.310 --> 00:17:53.230
Please. move aside.

314
00:17:53.520 --> 00:17:56.310
Mr. Qazi. there's been
a huge mistake.

315
00:17:56.350 --> 00:17:57.510
Please get me a divorce.

316
00:17:57.600 --> 00:17:58.390
Annul this wedding right now.

317
00:17:58.480 --> 00:17:59.560
Cancel it...
I'm ready to divorce her.

318
00:17:59.640 --> 00:18:02.930
Oh God. the wedding just happened
and you're already talking divorce?

319
00:18:03.270 --> 00:18:04.190
You need the girl's consent too.

320
00:18:04.270 --> 00:18:06.060
Listen. I beg to you.

321
00:18:06.140 --> 00:18:07.640
please divorce me.

322
00:18:07.730 --> 00:18:09.270
I can't go through with this marriage.

323
00:18:09.350 --> 00:18:10.640
What are you saying?

324
00:18:10.730 --> 00:18:12.150
How can you even say that?

325
00:18:12.980 --> 00:18:16.360
In front of everyone
and the Holy Quran.

326
00:18:16.770 --> 00:18:21.270
I've accepted you without
knowing a thing about you.

327
00:18:22.020 --> 00:18:24.730
And now you want to divorce me?

328
00:18:25.600 --> 00:18:29.100
Look. I've already been
divorced twice.

329
00:18:29.600 --> 00:18:31.220
If it happens again.

330
00:18:31.810 --> 00:18:34.310
I'll end my life on the train tracks!

331
00:18:35.100 --> 00:18:36.050
Listen...

332
00:18:36.140 --> 00:18:37.510
Someone stop her.

333
00:18:37.600 --> 00:18:39.800
- Ruhi!
- Stop. Ruhi!

334
00:18:40.560 --> 00:18:41.520
Stop!

335
00:18:41.890 --> 00:18:42.890
Stop. Ruhi!

336
00:18:48.310 --> 00:18:49.610
Ruhi!

337
00:18:50.640 --> 00:18:52.720
Stop!

338
00:19:18.890 --> 00:19:20.800
He'd come here
to marry my bride...

339
00:19:21.310 --> 00:19:22.270
There you go.

340
00:19:23.430 --> 00:19:24.930
I'll marry Saniya!

341
00:19:25.020 --> 00:19:25.730
Yes.

342
00:19:25.810 --> 00:19:26.810
Let's go.

343
00:19:31.270 --> 00:19:35.770
The number you have dialed
is out of coverage area.

344
00:19:35.850 --> 00:19:39.470
This Saniya. I swear...
never asks me before doing anything.

345
00:19:39.930 --> 00:19:41.640
Got me stuck here.
and God knows where she's disappeared to.

346
00:19:44.430 --> 00:19:46.350
Ouch.

347
00:20:24.390 --> 00:20:25.430
Meera?

348
00:20:27.270 --> 00:20:29.310
But... didn't I marry Ruhi?

349
00:20:33.430 --> 00:20:34.260
Have some tea.

350
00:20:34.310 --> 00:20:35.480
What are you doing here?

351
00:20:35.560 --> 00:20:37.060
Drink your tea. I'll tell you.

352
00:20:37.140 --> 00:20:40.430
- I don't want tea! Mom! Mom!
- Mohan!

353
00:20:40.560 --> 00:20:42.230
- Father!
- Mohan!

354
00:20:42.480 --> 00:20:43.400
What is all this?

355
00:20:43.770 --> 00:20:45.060
What is Meera doing here?

356
00:20:45.600 --> 00:20:46.350
Mom?

357
00:20:46.640 --> 00:20:48.100
You got married to her.

358
00:20:48.310 --> 00:20:50.400
I got married?! When?!

359
00:20:50.480 --> 00:20:52.690
You remember
when you got hit on the head?

360
00:20:52.770 --> 00:20:53.360
Yes?

361
00:20:53.430 --> 00:20:55.430
I'll tell you what happened after that.

362
00:20:56.430 --> 00:20:58.260
[Sanskrit Chants]

363
00:21:19.060 --> 00:21:22.400
You mean you knocked me out
and got me married?

364
00:21:22.810 --> 00:21:23.610
Why. Father?!

365
00:21:24.140 --> 00:21:27.390
Because I promised her father

366
00:21:27.480 --> 00:21:30.520
she'd be our daughter-in-law.

367
00:21:30.810 --> 00:21:32.860
Now you're married to Meera.

368
00:21:32.980 --> 00:21:34.270
She is your wife.

369
00:21:34.480 --> 00:21:36.770
So it's your responsibility
to keep her happy.

370
00:21:36.930 --> 00:21:37.800
Got it?

371
00:21:37.980 --> 00:21:38.610
Mohan. please. have some tea.

372
00:21:38.680 --> 00:21:40.180
Take it away! I don't want
to drink tea!

373
00:21:40.270 --> 00:21:42.310
Never mind. dear.
bring him some milk instead.

374
00:21:42.560 --> 00:21:45.360
It's your wedding night anyway.

375
00:21:45.430 --> 00:21:47.800
Nothing's happening tonight...
or ever!

376
00:21:47.930 --> 00:21:49.180
I don't accept this marriage!

377
00:21:49.890 --> 00:21:51.350
How can you not?

378
00:21:51.890 --> 00:21:53.470
We took the wedding vows around
the holy fire together.

379
00:21:53.730 --> 00:21:54.520
You tied this Mangalsutra
(wedding necklace) around my neck

380
00:21:54.600 --> 00:21:55.970
and filled your forehead with vermillion.

381
00:21:56.640 --> 00:21:58.640
I've accepted you as my husband
for seven lifetimes.

382
00:21:58.730 --> 00:22:00.360
Then give me a discount
and skip this one.

383
00:22:00.430 --> 00:22:02.600
Meet me in the next six. Happy?

384
00:22:04.100 --> 00:22:06.300
If you don't accept me.

385
00:22:08.230 --> 00:22:11.150
then I'll throw myself under a train.

386
00:22:12.180 --> 00:22:13.800
- Daughter-in-law!
- Meera!

387
00:22:14.310 --> 00:22:15.360
Daughter-in-law. stop!

388
00:22:15.770 --> 00:22:17.020
Meera. stop!

389
00:22:24.060 --> 00:22:25.060
Meera!!!

390
00:22:26.560 --> 00:22:28.440
Stop!!!

391
00:22:52.270 --> 00:22:54.230
Our daughter-in-law's so cultured.

392
00:22:55.020 --> 00:22:57.360
she even understands her
father-in-law's cough.

393
00:23:04.850 --> 00:23:06.100
Saniya. where the hell are you?

394
00:23:06.270 --> 00:23:07.650
- Do you know--
- I know everything.

395
00:23:07.730 --> 00:23:10.560
Our families will never accept
a Hindu-Muslim wedding.

396
00:23:10.640 --> 00:23:13.390
That's why I ran off to Goa
and became a Christian.

397
00:23:14.180 --> 00:23:15.010
You became a Christian?!

398
00:23:15.180 --> 00:23:17.300
Yes. there's a mass wedding
happening at a local church here.

399
00:23:17.600 --> 00:23:20.430
We can easily get married there.
so I signed us up.

400
00:23:20.520 --> 00:23:22.020
My name's Rosy.
and yours is Michael.

401
00:23:22.100 --> 00:23:23.430
I'm... I'm Michael?!

402
00:23:23.560 --> 00:23:25.940
Yes! Hurry up.
I'm sending you the address.

403
00:23:26.020 --> 00:23:26.770
Wait. Saniya. at least hear me out--

404
00:23:26.850 --> 00:23:28.550
Hey. listen.
I'm switching my phone off.

405
00:23:28.640 --> 00:23:30.550
or my family will track me down.

406
00:23:30.640 --> 00:23:32.800
- Okay? Bye.
- Saniya. listen--

407
00:23:39.140 --> 00:23:41.350
So you couldn't even tell Saniya

408
00:23:41.430 --> 00:23:42.930
you accidentally married someone else.
that too twice?

409
00:23:43.020 --> 00:23:44.310
No. she never listens!

410
00:23:44.430 --> 00:23:45.470
This is absurd.

411
00:23:45.980 --> 00:23:47.190
From Mohan you became Mehmood...

412
00:23:47.270 --> 00:23:48.730
and now from Mehmood you'll turn
into what. Michael?

413
00:23:48.810 --> 00:23:50.440
Yeah. I'll do anything for love.

414
00:23:50.600 --> 00:23:51.890
Just book me a ticket to Goa.

415
00:23:53.640 --> 00:23:54.800
Mehmood!

416
00:23:55.980 --> 00:23:57.360
Hey. Mehmood!

417
00:23:58.350 --> 00:24:00.350
- Mehmood!
- Who's Mehmood here?

418
00:24:00.810 --> 00:24:01.860
You are.

419
00:24:01.980 --> 00:24:02.980
- Hey!
- Mirza's here.

420
00:24:03.140 --> 00:24:04.510
- Mehmood!
- What's he doing here?

421
00:24:04.640 --> 00:24:05.470
Let's go find out.

422
00:24:05.850 --> 00:24:06.720
What now. Mr. Mirza?

423
00:24:06.810 --> 00:24:07.560
What's your problem this time?

424
00:24:07.640 --> 00:24:08.470
No problem as such...

425
00:24:08.560 --> 00:24:09.610
but you've been missing since
the wedding night.

426
00:24:09.680 --> 00:24:11.010
Ruhi's been waiting for you.
Come on. let's go.

427
00:24:11.140 --> 00:24:11.850
Let her wait.

428
00:24:11.930 --> 00:24:12.930
I didn't marry her willingly.

429
00:24:13.140 --> 00:24:14.140
you people trapped me in it.

430
00:24:14.270 --> 00:24:15.650
Who isn't trapped in marriage?

431
00:24:15.730 --> 00:24:18.270
Even the ones who marry by choice
end up feeling trapped.

432
00:24:18.810 --> 00:24:21.110
Hubby. your friend's
a married man now.

433
00:24:21.180 --> 00:24:22.970
Let him go to his wife at night.

434
00:24:23.060 --> 00:24:25.400
You can just watch videos on YouTube.

435
00:24:25.480 --> 00:24:27.020
I do the same... it's fun.

436
00:24:28.310 --> 00:24:29.940
- Let's go.
- You go. I'll come later.

437
00:24:30.020 --> 00:24:30.900
Let's go. come on.

438
00:24:30.980 --> 00:24:32.440
He'll come. Mr. Mirza.

439
00:24:32.520 --> 00:24:35.150
It's not like he's got a second wife
waiting for him somewhere.

440
00:24:35.230 --> 00:24:36.020
Second wife?!

441
00:24:36.100 --> 00:24:37.850
He's kidding! You go ahead.
I'll be there soon.

442
00:24:38.020 --> 00:24:38.770
Leave already?

443
00:24:38.850 --> 00:24:39.640
I'm your father-in-law.

444
00:24:39.770 --> 00:24:41.020
I came to your restaurant
for the first time...

445
00:24:41.100 --> 00:24:42.010
at least offer me some coffee.

446
00:24:42.100 --> 00:24:43.470
Coffee's laced with poison these days.

447
00:24:43.680 --> 00:24:44.550
- You still want some?
- No. thank you.

448
00:24:44.640 --> 00:24:45.640
One coffee--

449
00:24:45.980 --> 00:24:47.400
No. poison gives me acidity.

450
00:24:47.480 --> 00:24:48.730
Maybe next time.
You're coming with me.

451
00:24:48.850 --> 00:24:49.640
- I'll join you later. You go ahead.
- Come on. come on.

452
00:24:49.730 --> 00:24:50.360
We're coming.
we're coming. you carry on.

453
00:24:50.430 --> 00:24:50.970
Let's go.

454
00:24:51.060 --> 00:24:51.520
Go on. man!

455
00:24:51.600 --> 00:24:52.680
- Come on!
- Go!

456
00:24:59.230 --> 00:25:02.440
"Show some respect.
I even have a car."

457
00:25:02.810 --> 00:25:04.270
Does having a car earn you respect?

458
00:25:04.680 --> 00:25:05.550
I don't know.

459
00:25:05.810 --> 00:25:06.900
You too should buy one then.

460
00:25:08.430 --> 00:25:09.890
Such a delicious meal.

461
00:25:10.980 --> 00:25:12.730
We've got such a cultured
daughter-in-law.

462
00:25:12.810 --> 00:25:14.730
and your son's gone missing.

463
00:25:15.730 --> 00:25:17.020
Welcome. welcome. welcome.

464
00:25:17.140 --> 00:25:18.220
Where the hell have you been?

465
00:25:18.480 --> 00:25:21.060
Your wife's been waiting
for you since last night.

466
00:25:21.140 --> 00:25:23.140
Did I tell you to whack me on
the head and marry me off to her?

467
00:25:23.230 --> 00:25:24.400
You hit me so hard.
it bruised my brain!

468
00:25:24.480 --> 00:25:24.980
What?

469
00:25:25.060 --> 00:25:26.310
- I went to see a doctor.
- Hmm.

470
00:25:26.390 --> 00:25:27.180
Doctor?

471
00:25:27.270 --> 00:25:29.480
Yes. Tell him what the doctor said.

472
00:25:30.480 --> 00:25:31.310
What did the doctor say?

473
00:25:31.430 --> 00:25:32.800
You tell him!

474
00:25:33.480 --> 00:25:34.770
I was waiting outside. you went in.

475
00:25:34.850 --> 00:25:36.510
You tell him what he said.

476
00:25:36.730 --> 00:25:39.360
He said I need three
injections in Goa.

477
00:25:39.430 --> 00:25:40.430
- Goa?
- Yes.

478
00:25:40.520 --> 00:25:41.940
Yeah. I heard Goa too.

479
00:25:42.020 --> 00:25:43.440
Fine then. since you're going to Goa.

480
00:25:43.520 --> 00:25:44.730
take your wife with you.

481
00:25:44.810 --> 00:25:46.730
Make it a honeymoon.

482
00:25:46.890 --> 00:25:48.510
Who said I'm going for
a honeymoon?

483
00:25:48.600 --> 00:25:50.180
Didn't you hear
what your mother just said?

484
00:25:50.270 --> 00:25:52.360
That knock on the head made
you deaf too?

485
00:25:52.430 --> 00:25:54.470
Father. I cannot take her
to Goa with me.

486
00:25:54.600 --> 00:25:58.470
You will go to Goa
and she's going with you!

487
00:25:58.600 --> 00:25:59.550
Got it?

488
00:25:59.640 --> 00:26:01.600
Mom. should I start packing?

489
00:26:01.680 --> 00:26:04.180
Yes. and Hubby...

490
00:26:04.270 --> 00:26:05.440
book tickets for both.

491
00:26:05.520 --> 00:26:06.360
Yes. Mom.

492
00:26:06.430 --> 00:26:07.390
Thank you. Mom!

493
00:26:07.850 --> 00:26:09.140
You're lucky...

494
00:26:09.310 --> 00:26:11.770
he's taking you
to Goa for honeymoon.

495
00:26:12.390 --> 00:26:15.100
He just took me upstairs
for our honeymoon.

496
00:26:15.180 --> 00:26:18.300
Well. I got great results
just by going upstairs.

497
00:26:18.350 --> 00:26:20.010
so why waste money on
a trip to Goa?

498
00:26:20.100 --> 00:26:22.180
But you two will go to Goa...

499
00:26:22.270 --> 00:26:24.270
and take her with you.

500
00:26:24.430 --> 00:26:26.470
- Gubby.
- Uncle. it's Hubby.

501
00:26:26.560 --> 00:26:28.440
Yeah. Gubby. Hubby.
Chubby. whatever.

502
00:26:28.560 --> 00:26:30.060
Both the tickets
and send them to Goa.

503
00:26:31.100 --> 00:26:31.890
Fine.

504
00:26:38.310 --> 00:26:39.020
You are here.

505
00:26:39.140 --> 00:26:40.010
You called so many times.
I had to show up.

506
00:26:40.100 --> 00:26:40.890
"The number you're trying
to reach is switched off."

507
00:26:41.020 --> 00:26:41.940
You do this too?

508
00:26:42.020 --> 00:26:43.230
I can handle anything.

509
00:26:43.310 --> 00:26:44.650
Ever since she got married
and came here.

510
00:26:44.730 --> 00:26:46.690
she's been wearing that collar around her
neck just to avoid doing any work.

511
00:26:46.770 --> 00:26:48.230
Saniya's phone's still switched off.

512
00:26:48.310 --> 00:26:49.520
God knows where she's disappeared.

513
00:26:49.770 --> 00:26:52.060
If she'd stayed till the wedding.
she'd have married Mohan

514
00:26:52.140 --> 00:26:53.350
and we wouldn't be facing
this embarrassment.

515
00:26:53.430 --> 00:26:55.050
The kheer (sweet rice pudding)
and puris (fried flatbread) are ready.

516
00:26:55.480 --> 00:26:56.310
Here you go.

