<i>Ranjha found Heer. his soul's delight.</i>

2385
01:43:57.020 --> 01:44:02.730
<i>He found his destiny. his guiding light.</i>

2386
01:44:21.640 --> 01:44:29.050
<i>I want you near and nothing more.</i>

2387
01:44:32.100 --> 01:44:35.350
<i>May no sun scorch you as before.</i>

2388
01:44:35.430 --> 01:44:40.050
<i>I'll walk beside you.
as your shade evermore.</i>

2389
01:44:42.350 --> 01:44:44.930
<i>One lifetime can't contain my need.</i>

2390
01:44:45.020 --> 01:44:47.400
<i>I'll come again and again indeed.</i>

2391
01:44:47.480 --> 01:44:49.860
<i>If born a hundred times anew.</i>

2392
01:44:49.930 --> 01:44:55.470
<i>Each time I'll search. and find it's you.</i>

2393
01:44:55.770 --> 01:44:59.020
<i>I thought I'd lost what life could be.</i>

2394
01:45:00.850 --> 01:45:04.220
<i>But found my mate. my destiny.</i>

2395
01:45:06.060 --> 01:45:10.770
<i>The thirsty found a river deep.</i>

2396
01:45:11.140 --> 01:45:14.720
<i>The weary at last found relief.</i>

2397
