<i>The thirsty found a river deep.</i>

2406
01:45:51.980 --> 01:45:55.650
<i>The weary at last found relief.</i>

2407
01:45:56.890 --> 01:46:00.600
<i>Ranjha found Heer. his soul's delight.</i>

2408
01:46:02.020 --> 01:46:07.900
<i>He found his destiny. his guiding light.</i>

2409
01:46:40.060 --> 01:46:41.440
I love you. Mr. Manjeet.

2410
01:46:45.850 --> 01:46:48.220
She doesn't even remember she's Saniya

2411
01:46:48.560 --> 01:46:50.650
It's fine. at least she fell for me.

2412
01:46:52.600 --> 01:46:53.800
Damn it.

2413
01:46:53.930 --> 01:46:55.640
Ever since you found Saniya.

2414
01:46:56.020 --> 01:46:57.900
I've been stuck answering calls
from all three wives of yours.

2415
01:46:57.980 --> 01:46:59.190
You didn't tell them the truth. did you?

2416
01:46:59.810 --> 01:47:01.980
I told them something even
I don't understand.

2417
01:47:02.060 --> 01:47:03.060
What?

2418
01:47:04.680 --> 01:47:09.100
[Gibberish]

2419
01:47:14.020 --> 01:47:15.360
Manjeet. son.

2420
01:47:16.140 --> 01:47:19.760
ever since Simran saw you.
she hasn't stopped smiling.

2421
01:47:19.850 --> 01:47:21.640
The same goes for him. Aunty.

2422
01:47:21.730 --> 01:47:24.770
Before this. he was a wreck trying
to juggle three homes.

2423
01:47:24.850 --> 01:47:26.100
- Three homes?
- Three homes?

2424
01:47:26.180 --> 01:47:30.010
Yes... my home. his home and your home.

2425
01:47:30.140 --> 01:47:31.300
Yes.

2426
01:47:31.770 --> 01:47:34.770
So Simran. what have you decided?

2427
01:47:34.850 --> 01:47:36.100
Should we get you married to him?

2428
01:47:36.180 --> 01:47:38.430
I've already said "I love you" to him.

2429
01:47:38.560 --> 01:47:40.060
- Wow...
- What else can I say?

2430
01:47:40.600 --> 01:47:41.970
Say it two more times.

2431
01:47:42.430 --> 01:47:44.010
It takes three "I dos" to seal the deal.

2432
01:47:44.180 --> 01:47:45.050
Huh?

2433
01:47:45.140 --> 01:47:47.680
I went to a Muslim friend's wedding once.

2434
01:47:47.770 --> 01:47:49.310
I saw them say it three times.

2435
01:47:49.430 --> 01:47:50.470
Oh.

2436
01:47:50.640 --> 01:47:55.640
Son. we want you to come as the groom
in our ancestral car. as soon as possible.

2437
01:47:56.140 --> 01:47:57.720
Don't you think it's too small?

2438
01:47:57.810 --> 01:47:59.230
- Yes.
- This is its key.

2439
01:47:59.310 --> 01:48:00.940
Ah. the key.

2440
01:48:01.020 --> 01:48:02.730
I thought you meant
I had to come in this car.

2441
01:48:04.640 --> 01:48:05.680
Hello?

2442
01:48:05.810 --> 01:48:06.480
Hello?

2443
01:48:06.560 --> 01:48:11.650
[Gibberish]

2444
01:48:15.060 --> 01:48:17.650
Fine. you're in Dubai.
but at least pick up the phone. Michael.

2445
01:48:17.680 --> 01:48:19.010
He's still in Dubai.

2446
01:48:20.560 --> 01:48:23.560
Sir. we got CCTV footage
from that church in Goa.

2447
01:48:24.480 --> 01:48:25.650
Zoom in.

2448
01:48:27.640 --> 01:48:28.640
Zoom in further.

2449
01:48:44.810 --> 01:48:46.900
We can see a girl get kidnapped.

2450
01:48:47.020 --> 01:48:48.270
- Hmm.
- Have a look.

2451
01:48:49.600 --> 01:48:51.640
The girl was there that day
at the church to get married.

2452
01:48:51.890 --> 01:48:53.640
She had enrolled herself as Rosy.

2453
01:48:53.730 --> 01:48:54.980
Who was she going to marry?

2454
01:48:55.060 --> 01:48:56.060
Someone named Michael.

2455
01:48:57.140 --> 01:48:58.140
Michael?

2456
01:48:58.350 --> 01:48:59.300
Yes. sir.

2457
01:48:59.390 --> 01:49:01.180
That day two Michaels showed up
to get married.

2458
01:49:01.730 --> 01:49:02.610
Okay.

2459
01:49:02.850 --> 01:49:03.890
And the kidnapper?

2460
01:49:04.310 --> 01:49:05.480
We have him waiting outside.

2461
01:49:06.890 --> 01:49:07.890
Come with me.

2462
01:49:12.600 --> 01:49:13.510
Where's Rosy?

2463
01:49:15.230 --> 01:49:16.230
Who's Rosy. sir?

2464
01:49:18.100 --> 01:49:20.430
The girl you kidnapped from the church.

2465
01:49:20.890 --> 01:49:22.720
That wasn't Rosy. sir. that was Saniya.

2466
01:49:22.810 --> 01:49:23.900
Saniya?

2467
01:49:24.600 --> 01:49:25.800
How did she become Rosy?

2468
01:49:25.890 --> 01:49:27.350
I don't know. sir.

2469
01:49:28.850 --> 01:49:31.100
She went there as Rosy to marry Mehmood.

2470
01:49:31.180 --> 01:49:32.850
So she went there to marry you?

2471
01:49:33.350 --> 01:49:34.390
No. the other Mehmood.

2472
01:49:35.520 --> 01:49:37.860
But in the register it says that
she came there to marry Michael.

2473
01:49:37.930 --> 01:49:39.680
But sir. she loved Mehmood.

2474
01:49:39.770 --> 01:49:40.730
So she loved you.

2475
01:49:40.810 --> 01:49:42.650
No. the other Mehmood.

2476
01:49:43.390 --> 01:49:46.760
So before Michael.
she loved another Mehmood?

2477
01:49:46.850 --> 01:49:49.260
No sir. first she loved Mohan.

2478
01:49:49.730 --> 01:49:50.860
So two men loved her...?

2479
01:49:50.930 --> 01:49:53.010
Mohan and the other Mehmood?

2480
01:49:53.100 --> 01:49:54.890
No sir. only one man truly loved her.

2481
01:49:54.980 --> 01:49:57.440
Didn't you say first Mohan loved her.

2482
01:49:57.520 --> 01:49:59.060
then later the other Mehmood loved her too?

2483
01:49:59.140 --> 01:49:59.760
Yes. sir.

2484
01:49:59.850 --> 01:50:02.550
So Mohan and the other Mehmood...
how many men is that?

2485
01:50:02.680 --> 01:50:03.260
One. sir.

2486
01:50:03.350 --> 01:50:05.050
I'll slap you senseless.

2487
01:50:06.230 --> 01:50:10.230
Mohan and the other Mehmood...
that's two men. right?

2488
01:50:10.430 --> 01:50:11.640
One. sir.

2489
01:50:13.310 --> 01:50:14.730
Are you even following what he's saying?

2490
01:50:14.850 --> 01:50:16.800
Sir. you're the inspector.

2491
01:50:16.980 --> 01:50:19.940
if you can't. then how can I?
I'm just a constable!

2492
01:50:22.060 --> 01:50:26.360
Look. this station has me.
Sukumar. and Sanjay.

2493
01:50:26.520 --> 01:50:27.480
How many men's that?

2494
01:50:27.770 --> 01:50:29.190
- Three. sir.
- Good.

2495
01:50:29.810 --> 01:50:33.480
Now if the ones
who loved Saniya are Mohan. Mehmood.

2496
01:50:33.810 --> 01:50:35.980
- no. the other Mehmood and Michael...
- the other Mehmood.

2497
01:50:36.060 --> 01:50:37.400
How many men's that?

2498
01:50:38.680 --> 01:50:39.470
One. sir.

2499
01:50:39.560 --> 01:50:43.650
You idiot. Mohan. the other Mehmood

2500
01:50:43.730 --> 01:50:46.940
and Michael
are three different people not one!

2501
01:50:47.020 --> 01:50:49.560
Are you high or what?

2502
01:50:49.640 --> 01:50:51.970
Sir. this man just said the same thing...

2503
01:50:52.180 --> 01:50:53.430
Mohan. Mehmood. and Michael

2504
01:50:53.520 --> 01:50:54.650
- are all the same person.
- Yes.

2505
01:50:54.980 --> 01:50:57.310
Is everyone high or what?

2506
01:50:57.480 --> 01:50:58.400
Who are you?

2507
01:50:58.640 --> 01:50:59.640
Sir...

2508
01:51:00.390 --> 01:51:03.930
Sir. I'm the Physical Training Instructor
at SSG International School.

2509
01:51:04.020 --> 01:51:04.730
Hmm.

2510
01:51:04.850 --> 01:51:09.760
That man donated blood three times.
under three names:

2511
01:51:10.230 --> 01:51:12.480
Mohan. Mehmood. and Michael.

2512
01:51:12.850 --> 01:51:14.720
He is married to three women.

2513
01:51:14.810 --> 01:51:15.980
Each one claims him as her husband.

2514
01:51:16.100 --> 01:51:17.430
I can show you their photos.

2515
01:51:17.520 --> 01:51:18.400
Then show it.

2516
01:51:20.140 --> 01:51:23.050
Sir. he's a cheat.

2517
01:51:23.270 --> 01:51:27.690
He offered me Rs. 50.000 to stay quiet.

2518
01:51:28.060 --> 01:51:30.230
But sir. let me tell you.

2519
01:51:30.310 --> 01:51:33.810
forget Rs. 50.000.
he didn't even give me 50 paisa!

2520
01:51:33.890 --> 01:51:34.930
No honesty left in this world. I tell you!

2521
01:51:35.020 --> 01:51:36.360
Just show the damn photo!

2522
01:51:36.770 --> 01:51:37.690
I'll show it to you. sir.

2523
01:51:37.770 --> 01:51:39.110
I couldn't find it.

2524
01:51:39.180 --> 01:51:40.180
Here it is. sir.

2525
01:51:41.350 --> 01:51:42.680
His first wife. Meera.

2526
01:51:42.890 --> 01:51:46.050
Sir. this is his second wife. Ruhi.

2527
01:51:46.480 --> 01:51:49.020
And this is third wife...

2528
01:51:49.560 --> 01:51:51.020
- Jenny?
- Yes. Jenny.

2529
01:51:52.230 --> 01:51:55.150
And this...
this is the man I was talking about.

2530
01:51:55.980 --> 01:51:56.940
Michael.

2531
01:51:57.100 --> 01:51:58.050
Yes.

2532
01:51:58.560 --> 01:51:59.610
One man.

2533
01:52:09.810 --> 01:52:11.480
You shouldn't have done this.

2534
01:52:11.560 --> 01:52:14.980
I wouldn't have. sir.
if he'd just given me Rs. 50.000.

2535
01:52:16.980 --> 01:52:18.400
Are we facing a power failure or what?

2536
01:52:18.480 --> 01:52:19.440
Take him away.

2537
01:52:22.600 --> 01:52:24.390
And call these three to the police station.

2538
01:52:24.600 --> 01:52:26.100
Who. Mohan. Mehmood and Michael?

2539
01:52:27.140 --> 01:52:28.390
All the three girls!

2540
01:52:30.270 --> 01:52:31.230
Forget it.

2541
01:52:33.020 --> 01:52:34.110
I'll handle it.

2542
01:52:38.020 --> 01:52:39.190
Sir. here's your ring.

2543
01:52:42.890 --> 01:52:44.470
It's beautiful. ma'am. thank you.

2544
01:52:45.310 --> 01:52:46.610
- Would you like a carry bag?
- No. I'm just going to put it on right away.

2545
01:52:46.640 --> 01:52:47.550
Thank you.

2546
01:52:48.980 --> 01:52:50.480
Mohan's been missing for days.

2547
01:52:50.730 --> 01:52:52.360
Even his in-laws are asking now.

2548
01:52:52.520 --> 01:52:53.230
Hello?

2549
01:52:53.350 --> 01:52:57.930
[Gibberish]

2550
01:52:58.020 --> 01:52:59.110
Shut up!

2551
01:52:59.180 --> 01:53:02.800
[Gibberish]

2552
01:53:02.890 --> 01:53:04.550
[Gibberish]

2553
01:53:04.640 --> 01:53:05.180
Shut up!

2554
01:53:05.270 --> 01:53:06.690
[Gibberish]

2555
01:53:07.350 --> 01:53:08.640
He hung up on me!

2556
01:53:08.730 --> 01:53:10.110
Who're you yelling at?

2557
01:53:10.890 --> 01:53:14.010
Mohan's in Dubai. dear.

2558
01:53:14.140 --> 01:53:17.050
I think he eloped with Saniya.

2559
01:53:17.140 --> 01:53:18.180
Saniya?!

2560
01:53:18.730 --> 01:53:22.270
Yeah. I think it's because
of her he turned into Mehmood.

2561
01:53:22.430 --> 01:53:24.390
What nonsense! Don't say that!

2562
01:53:24.480 --> 01:53:25.480
Why shouldn't I?

2563
01:53:25.600 --> 01:53:29.600
Remember the other day.
we found a Muslim cap in his clothes.

2564
01:53:29.850 --> 01:53:32.890
And every time someone shouts.
"Mehmood! Mehmood!".

2565
01:53:32.980 --> 01:53:34.770
it's Mohan who runs out!

2566
01:53:34.850 --> 01:53:37.220
Mehmood! Mehmood!

2567
01:53:37.310 --> 01:53:38.400
Heard that?

2568
01:53:38.890 --> 01:53:41.350
Let me go find out who it is.

2569
01:53:43.640 --> 01:53:44.470
Mehmood!

2570
01:53:44.600 --> 01:53:45.180
You?

2571
01:53:45.270 --> 01:53:45.860
Yeah. me.

2572
01:53:45.930 --> 01:53:47.600
Who are you calling Mehmood?

2573
01:53:47.640 --> 01:53:48.680
My son-in-law.

2574
01:53:48.770 --> 01:53:49.480
Who's your son-in-law?

2575
01:53:49.560 --> 01:53:50.480
Your son.

2576
01:53:50.560 --> 01:53:51.520
- Mohan.
- Yes.

2577
01:53:51.600 --> 01:53:52.850
How is Mohan your son-in-law?

2578
01:53:52.930 --> 01:53:54.140
He married Ruhi.

2579
01:53:54.230 --> 01:53:55.810
He married Meera.

2580
01:53:55.890 --> 01:53:56.680
He married Ruhi.

2581
01:53:56.770 --> 01:53:58.270
He married Meera.

2582
01:53:58.350 --> 01:53:59.800
Looks like he married both of them.

2583
01:53:59.890 --> 01:54:00.890
He got married twice?

2584
01:54:01.180 --> 01:54:02.720
I'll break his bones.

2585
01:54:02.810 --> 01:54:03.650
I'll break his head.

2586
01:54:03.680 --> 01:54:04.470
- Get lost!
- You get lost!

2587
01:54:04.560 --> 01:54:05.650
- Get lost!
- You get lost!

2588
01:54:05.730 --> 01:54:08.360
Stop. stop. stop...
do you even know where Mohan is?

2589
01:54:08.430 --> 01:54:09.640
- Dubai!
- Dubai!

2590
01:54:09.730 --> 01:54:11.480
No. he's in Bhopal.

2591
01:54:11.560 --> 01:54:12.730
- In Bhopal?
- Yes.

2592
01:54:12.810 --> 01:54:16.900
He just bought a diamond ring
with my credit card for Women's Day.

2593
01:54:16.980 --> 01:54:19.020
Who's getting the ring this time?

2594
01:54:19.100 --> 01:54:20.220
How would I know?

2595
01:54:20.310 --> 01:54:21.610
I just got a message from DB Mall.

2596
01:54:21.640 --> 01:54:22.220
DB Mall?

2597
01:54:22.310 --> 01:54:23.860
- Let's go. let's go. let's go.
- Please. hurry up.

2598
01:54:23.980 --> 01:54:26.150
I am. dear. I am.

2599
01:54:42.180 --> 01:54:43.050
Oh shit!

2600
01:54:57.520 --> 01:54:58.480
Meera?

2601
01:54:59.140 --> 01:54:59.800
Hey!

2602
01:54:59.890 --> 01:55:00.430
Jenny!

2603
01:55:00.520 --> 01:55:01.560
- Hi!
- Hi!

2604
01:55:01.600 --> 01:55:02.640
How are you?

2605
01:55:02.680 --> 01:55:04.100
I'm good. How about you?

2606
01:55:04.230 --> 01:55:05.520
- I'm fine. thank you.
- Hi!

2607
01:55:05.600 --> 01:55:07.510
What brings you two here?

2608
01:55:07.600 --> 01:55:08.680
Hi!

2609
01:55:08.980 --> 01:55:10.400
My brother called me.

2610
01:55:10.480 --> 01:55:12.360
I have called these two here as well.

2611
01:55:12.930 --> 01:55:14.100
Hello Meera. hi Ruhi.

2612
01:55:14.230 --> 01:55:15.520
Inspector David D'Costa.

2613
01:55:15.600 --> 01:55:16.640
Hello.

2614
01:55:17.890 --> 01:55:21.220
Brother. how do you know them?

2615
01:55:21.350 --> 01:55:22.600
I don't. actually.

2616
01:55:22.730 --> 01:55:24.770
But the police found some information

2617
01:55:24.850 --> 01:55:26.930
which I wanted to share it
with all three of you. together.

2618
01:55:28.480 --> 01:55:31.020
Excuse me. sir.
could you please move to the next table?

2619
01:55:32.350 --> 01:55:35.100
Son. can you too sit over there.
I need to talk to them.

2620
01:55:35.600 --> 01:55:36.430
Come. Jenny.

2621
01:55:45.980 --> 01:55:47.610
- He is your brother?
- Yes.

2622
01:55:48.480 --> 01:55:49.440
Yes.

2623
01:55:49.890 --> 01:55:51.180
What information?

2624
01:55:53.390 --> 01:55:56.010
Jenny. I could've told you at home.

2625
01:55:57.060 --> 01:56:00.400
but I thought that it'd would hurt
you less if you find out

2626
01:56:00.480 --> 01:56:02.440
about it in front of them.

2627
01:56:02.930 --> 01:56:04.260
Can you just come to the point?

2628
01:56:04.350 --> 01:56:05.640
Yes. why are you beating around the bush?

2629
01:56:05.730 --> 01:56:06.610
What's wrong?

2630
01:56:06.980 --> 01:56:09.650
I'm sure you three have
your husband's photos with you right now.

2631
01:56:09.730 --> 01:56:11.190
- Yeah. we do.
- On your mobile phones?

2632
01:56:11.270 --> 01:56:12.020
- Yes.
- Yes.

2633
01:56:12.100 --> 01:56:13.510
Please show them to each other.

2634
01:56:17.100 --> 01:56:18.050
Mohan Sharma.

2635
01:56:18.140 --> 01:56:19.010
Mehmood.

2636
01:56:21.020 --> 01:56:22.310
That's my Michael.

2637
01:56:22.810 --> 01:56:24.150
- What kind of a stupid joke is this?
- That's Michael!

2638
01:56:24.230 --> 01:56:25.360
- That's Mohan.
- That's Michael!

2639
01:56:25.850 --> 01:56:27.260
He's Mehmood. my husband.

2640
01:56:27.350 --> 01:56:29.680
- This is my husband. Mohan Sharma!
- What nonsense!

2641
01:56:29.770 --> 01:56:31.610
- He's my husband. Michael.
- Are you crazy?

2642
01:56:31.640 --> 01:56:33.430
- No. he's my husband.
- You mad or what?

2643
01:56:33.520 --> 01:56:34.360
That's Michael.

2644
01:56:34.430 --> 01:56:36.260
That's Mohan.
You think I wouldn't recognize my husband?

2645
01:56:36.350 --> 01:56:37.140
It's Michael.

2646
01:56:37.230 --> 01:56:38.400
- What are you saying?
- This is my Michael.

2647
01:56:38.480 --> 01:56:39.730
You think I wouldn't recognize my husband?

2648
01:56:39.810 --> 01:56:40.610
I wouldn't know my husband?

2649
01:56:40.640 --> 01:56:41.300
Just because we got married

2650
01:56:41.390 --> 01:56:43.390
on the same day doesn't mean
we got married to the same guy.

2651
01:56:43.480 --> 01:56:44.940
- Please...
- Who said we got married to the same guy?

2652
01:56:45.020 --> 01:56:46.520
- That is right.
- That's Michael.

2653
01:56:47.140 --> 01:56:49.600
That's why I called you three here
to tell the truth.

2654
01:56:49.680 --> 01:56:50.600
What's the truth?

2655
01:56:50.680 --> 01:56:55.300
He's your Mehmood.
your Mohan. and your Michael.

2656
01:56:55.390 --> 01:56:56.680
That's impossible.

2657
01:56:56.810 --> 01:56:58.810
- I'll call him right away.
- This man married

2658
01:56:59.350 --> 01:57:00.470
and deceived all three of you.

2659
01:57:00.600 --> 01:57:02.640
- No. I'll call Mohan right away.
- Give it to me.

2660
01:57:02.730 --> 01:57:03.770
- This is not possible.
- How is this possible?

2661
01:57:03.850 --> 01:57:05.510
Michael can't do this to me.

2662
01:57:06.100 --> 01:57:08.510
I couldn't believe it either. but...

2663
01:57:10.890 --> 01:57:11.890
Jenny?

2664
01:57:12.310 --> 01:57:13.190
Are you alright?

2665
01:57:13.350 --> 01:57:16.470
Jenny. please.
Please. breathe in. breathe in.

2666
01:57:16.770 --> 01:57:17.940
Please. breathe in.

2667
01:57:18.020 --> 01:57:19.060
It's alright.

2668
01:57:19.140 --> 01:57:20.180
It's going to be fine.

2669
01:57:20.310 --> 01:57:21.560
Take deep breaths.

2670
01:57:21.680 --> 01:57:23.930
- Jenny! Jenny! Jenny!
- How can I help?

2671
01:57:24.020 --> 01:57:25.690
- Doctor! Do we have a doctor here?
- Help!

2672
01:57:25.770 --> 01:57:27.810
- Somebody please help!
- Doctor! Please. call an ambulance.

2673
01:57:27.890 --> 01:57:29.260
- Get some water.
- Water!

2674
01:57:29.350 --> 01:57:31.600
- Move back. everyone.
- Give her some space.

2675
01:57:31.730 --> 01:57:32.980
Please. give her some space.

2676
01:57:33.060 --> 01:57:34.110
Give her some space.

2677
01:57:34.180 --> 01:57:35.600
- Water! Water!
- Please. give her some space.

2678
01:57:35.680 --> 01:57:37.010
Please. give her some space.

2679
01:57:37.140 --> 01:57:38.800
- Move back!
- Please. move back.

2680
01:57:41.600 --> 01:57:42.550
- Water!
- Oh. thank God!

2681
01:57:42.640 --> 01:57:44.300
Jenny. are you alright?

2682
01:57:45.600 --> 01:57:46.600
She's better.

2683
01:57:46.640 --> 01:57:47.640
Michael...

2684
01:57:48.100 --> 01:57:49.470
I won't spare Michael.

2685
01:57:51.560 --> 01:57:52.400
Thanks. sir.

2686
01:57:54.100 --> 01:57:55.600
My phone. my phone. my phone.

2687
01:57:56.140 --> 01:57:57.390
- I'll hand it to you. sir.
- Put it to my ear.

2688
01:57:59.310 --> 01:58:01.110
[Gibberish]

2689
01:58:01.180 --> 01:58:02.930
It's me. Where are you?

2690
01:58:03.020 --> 01:58:04.730
Trying on new outfits
for your wedding. bro.

2691
01:58:04.810 --> 01:58:06.400
