2692
01:58:06.560 --> 01:58:09.360
D.D. told all my three wives
that I'm Mohan. Mehmood. and Michael.

2693
01:58:09.430 --> 01:58:10.260
What are you saying?

2694
01:58:10.350 --> 01:58:11.800
You get out of there before they find out

2695
01:58:11.890 --> 01:58:14.350
I'm getting married
