2709
01:58:43.140 --> 01:58:44.100
What more could I ask for?

2710
01:58:45.770 --> 01:58:47.520
I used to think you were
a troublemaking devil.

2711
01:58:48.270 --> 01:58:52.190
but you proved kids really are angels.

2712
01:58:52.810 --> 01:58:53.810
Love you. son.

2713
01:58:53.890 --> 01:58:54.600
Thank you.

2714
01:58:54.730 --> 01:58:56.560
Now go. your fourth one is waiting.

2715
01:58:56.890 --> 01:58:58.100
Yeah. bye.

2716
01:58:59.310 --> 01:59:00.940
Hey Rapido. where are you?

2717
01:59:01.020 --> 01:59:03.110
Come fast. I'm waiting!

2718
01:59:04.310 --> 01:59:05.690
Where do you want to go?

2719
01:59:05.770 --> 01:59:07.060
You want us to drop you somewhere?

2720
01:59:07.140 --> 01:59:08.220
You two?

2721
01:59:08.310 --> 01:59:09.310
Where's Mohan?

2722
01:59:09.430 --> 01:59:09.970
Where is he?

2723
01:59:10.060 --> 01:59:11.730
- I-I'll go find out.
- Where's Mehmood?

2724
01:59:11.810 --> 01:59:12.980
- I'll check and be right back.
- Hey!

2725
01:59:13.060 --> 01:59:13.940
He's gone to find out.

2726
01:59:14.020 --> 01:59:14.860
Gone to find out?

2727
01:59:15.180 --> 01:59:17.220
We came here to ask him!

2728
01:59:17.430 --> 01:59:18.300
