2729
01:59:18.430 --> 01:59:19.510
Someone... Hubby!

2730
01:59:19.770 --> 01:59:21.270
Ask Hubby! He would know!

2731
01:59:21.560 --> 01:59:22.900
- Where's Michael. Hubby?
- Let's ask him!

2732
01:59:22.980 --> 01:59:24.400
- Where's Michael?
- Hubby. listen...!

2733
01:59:24.480 --> 01:59:26.810
- I'll go and ask! One second!
- Hubby! Hubby. wait!

2734
01:59:26.890 --> 01:59:27.760
I'm not going anywhere.

2735
01:59:27.850 --> 01:59:28.930
- Hubby. stop!
- I'll be right back!

2736
01:59:29.020 --> 01:59:30.110
- Hubby!
- Hubby!

2737
01:59:30.890 --> 01:59:32.220
- Stop him! Where is he going?
- Oh my God.

2738
01:59:32.310 --> 01:59:33.860
I've got his father waiting outside
and his wives chasing me inside!

2739
01:59:33.930 --> 01:59:35.010
- Hubby!
- Hubby!

2740
01:59:35.100 --> 01:59:35.640
Run!

2741
01:59:35.680 --> 01:59:37.510
Ma'am. look over there. that's Hubby!

2742
01:59:37.600 --> 01:59:38.680
This is my husband.

2743
01:59:39.100 --> 01:59:39.890
Hubby!

2744
01:59:39.980 --> 01:59:43.230
I told you he will get thrashed one day.

2745
01:59:43.310 --> 01:59:45.400
As you sow. so reap so shall.

2746
01:59:45.480 --> 01:59:47.270
- Yes. ma'am.
- Record it. Film it right now.

2747
01:59:47.520 --> 01:59:48.560
- Hubby. wait. wait...
- Brother!

2748
01:59:48.600 --> 01:59:50.100
- I just want to talk...
- Hubby...

2749
01:59:50.180 --> 01:59:51.100
- Hubby. stop.
- Come on!

2750
01:59:51.520 --> 01:59:52.440
Follow me!

2751
01:59:52.600 --> 01:59:53.890
Hubby. please stop.

2752
01:59:54.140 --> 01:59:54.720
Get him!

2753
01:59:54.810 --> 01:59:57.270
Surleen. I'm sending you
a video about your guy.

2754
01:59:58.140 --> 02:00:00.140
You had a close shave. This guy is doomed!

2755
02:00:00.230 --> 02:00:02.150
Stop! Hubby. stop!

2756
02:00:04.480 --> 02:00:05.810
Stop! Stop!

2757
02:00:06.180 --> 02:00:08.140
