2759
02:00:12.350 --> 02:00:13.760
Stop! Stop! Guppy. stop!

2760
02:00:14.730 --> 02:00:15.690
Hey...

2761
02:00:15.770 --> 02:00:17.440
Give me that. Where are the bullets?

2762
02:00:17.520 --> 02:00:18.190
Where are the bullets?

2763
02:00:18.270 --> 02:00:19.690
