- Let's go.

2764
02:00:19.770 --> 02:00:23.650
- Hurry up and hop on.
- Start the scooter first.

2765
02:00:23.730 --> 02:00:25.480
Let's go. let's go. let's go.

2766
02:00:25.770 --> 02:00:27.690
Get him! Get him!

2767
02:00:41.560 --> 02:00:43.400
Get out of my way. Aunty! Move away!

2768
02:00:43.520 --> 02:00:44.270
Hey!

2769
02:00:44.350 --> 02:00:45.220
He has lost it!

2770
02:00:45.310 --> 02:00:46.230
Hubby!

2771
02:00:48.390 --> 02:00:49.220
Hey!

2772
02:00:50.680 --> 02:00:51.470
Who are those two guys?

2773
02:00:51.560 --> 02:00:53.810
- That's my Abba's scooter.
- This way...

2774
02:00:53.980 --> 02:00:55.230
That's my Abba.

2775
02:00:57.310 --> 02:00:58.980
That's my father-in-law...
the one using the gun.

2776
02:00:59.060 --> 02:00:59.900
Father-in-law?

2777
02:01:00.520 --> 02:01:01.480
Stop it. guys!

2778
02:01:01.560 --> 02:01:02.770
Where're you aiming?

2779
02:01:02.850 --> 02:01:04.350
At the tyre.

2780
02:01:04.600 --> 02:01:05.930
Then aim at the balloon.

2781
02:01:06.020 --> 02:01:07.270
- The balloon?
- Yes.

2782
02:01:07.350 --> 02:01:08.550
Then you'll hit the tyre.

2783
02:01:08.640 --> 02:01:10.140
Direct hit!

2784
02:01:10.230 --> 02:01:12.730
And we have a blast!

2785
02:01:15.350 --> 02:01:16.800
We've a flat tyre.

2786
02:01:17.520 --> 02:01:19.650
Stop. He ran away.

2787
02:01:19.680 --> 02:01:21.930
Serves them right.
They ended up having a flat tyre.

2788
02:01:22.020 --> 02:01:23.770
- We can help them. right?
- Please.

2789
02:01:23.850 --> 02:01:25.050
- Why? Why?
- Let's give them a lift.

2790
02:01:25.140 --> 02:01:26.260
He's my father-in-law.

2791
02:01:26.350 --> 02:01:27.680
- He's my Abba.
- Alright. alright.

2792
02:01:27.980 --> 02:01:29.900
Stop! Stop! Stop!

2793
02:01:30.060 --> 02:01:30.690
Stop!

2794
02:01:31.350 --> 02:01:32.510
- Stop!
- Father!

2795
02:01:32.850 --> 02:01:35.260
Meera? What are you doing in there?

2796
02:01:35.350 --> 02:01:35.970
Ruhi?

2797
02:01:36.060 --> 02:01:37.650
What are you doing in a police jeep?

2798
02:01:37.730 --> 02:01:39.190
We are following Hubby.

2799
02:01:39.270 --> 02:01:40.730
Father. you know what Mohan did?

2800
02:01:40.810 --> 02:01:43.940
I know. that idiot got married twice.

2801
02:01:44.020 --> 02:01:45.150
Not twice... thrice.

2802
02:01:45.310 --> 02:01:46.980
- Thrice?
- His third wife is my sister...

2803
02:01:47.230 --> 02:01:47.980
From me.

2804
02:01:48.100 --> 02:01:49.140
God bless you. dear.

2805
02:01:49.230 --> 02:01:50.690
May you have a happy married life.

2806
02:01:51.020 --> 02:01:51.730
Huh?

2807
02:01:51.850 --> 02:01:52.800
Can't help it.

2808
02:01:52.980 --> 02:01:56.110
I'm used to giving blessings
to my daughter-in-law.

2809
02:01:56.180 --> 02:01:58.760
You want to bless.
I want to curse the rascal.

2810
02:01:58.850 --> 02:02:01.220
No cursing. now's the time to catch him
and give him a good thrashing.

2811
02:02:01.310 --> 02:02:01.980
Get in. quick.

2812
02:02:02.060 --> 02:02:02.690
Let's go. let's go. let's go.

2813
02:02:02.770 --> 02:02:04.020
Let's go. let's go. let's go.

2814
02:02:05.100 --> 02:02:05.850
Guppy!

2815
02:02:05.930 --> 02:02:07.220
Someone stop him!

2816
02:02:07.310 --> 02:02:08.480
Stop!

2817
02:02:08.600 --> 02:02:10.180
Drive faster. Brother!

2818
02:02:10.270 --> 02:02:11.650
They will fall.

2819
02:02:11.730 --> 02:02:12.560
Stop!

2820
02:02:12.640 --> 02:02:13.760
- Overtake him and bring him to a halt!
- Stop!

2821
02:02:13.850 --> 02:02:14.760
Guppy!

2822
02:02:14.850 --> 02:02:15.640
Stop!

2823
02:02:15.730 --> 02:02:17.400
- Overtake him and bring him to a halt!
- Guppy!

2824
02:02:17.730 --> 02:02:18.690
Stop!

2825
02:02:18.770 --> 02:02:20.110
Guppy!

2826
02:02:20.430 --> 02:02:21.680
Stop!

2827
02:02:22.140 --> 02:02:23.220
Stop!

2828
02:02:23.770 --> 02:02:24.400
Stop!

2829
02:02:24.480 --> 02:02:26.400
Catch him! What are you doing. catch him!

2830
02:02:26.480 --> 02:02:27.360
Stop!

2831
02:02:28.430 --> 02:02:29.260
What happened?

2832
02:02:29.350 --> 02:02:31.180
- Another flat tyre?
- Shit!

2833
02:02:31.270 --> 02:02:32.810
We're out of fuel.

2834
02:02:35.480 --> 02:02:38.810
This is exactly what you call being caught
between the devil and the deep blue sea.

2835
02:02:38.890 --> 02:02:41.140
Stuck between a rock and a hard place.

2836
02:02:41.230 --> 02:02:43.560
- Trouble everywhere.
- I'll take care of this.

2837
02:02:43.600 --> 02:02:44.760
There are a lot of us.
let's just take the bus.

2838
02:02:44.890 --> 02:02:48.720
The batsman will have
to hold his ground on the pitch.

2839
02:02:48.850 --> 02:02:50.100
Bam!

2840
02:02:50.560 --> 02:02:51.400
Stop! Stop! Stop!

2841
02:02:51.520 --> 02:02:53.190
Stop!
Stop! Stop! Please!

2842
02:02:54.230 --> 02:02:54.980
Please!

2843
02:02:55.060 --> 02:02:58.230
Sir... sir. it's an emergency.
We need your help.

2844
02:02:59.100 --> 02:03:01.220
You're the same guy who helped us before.

2845
02:03:01.350 --> 02:03:03.100
Looks like you're going
to be helping us all day today.

2846
02:03:03.180 --> 02:03:04.680
- Get in. everyone. he's a good man.
- Get in!

2847
02:03:04.770 --> 02:03:06.360
- Come on. quickly. Sit. sit. sit.
- Get in!

2848
02:03:06.430 --> 02:03:08.800
- Let's go. let's go. let's go!
- Wait. your veil...

2849
02:03:09.600 --> 02:03:11.050
- Abba!
- Move. move. get in.

2850
02:03:11.730 --> 02:03:13.810
Sir. there's a Sikh gentleman
on a scooter up ahead.

2851
02:03:13.890 --> 02:03:15.010
We are chasing him.

2852
02:03:15.140 --> 02:03:16.430
Please hurry.

2853
02:03:16.520 --> 02:03:17.440
Hurry up!

2854
02:03:17.560 --> 02:03:19.560
- He went this way!
- Go!

2855
02:03:19.640 --> 02:03:25.220
The batsman's surrounded from all sides.
Looks tough to get the winning runs now.

2856
02:03:25.310 --> 02:03:27.310
Still. where there's a will there's a way.

2857
02:03:27.390 --> 02:03:29.180
By the way. are you getting married today?

2858
02:03:29.270 --> 02:03:32.520
Yes. sir. I'm planning to...
hopefully it goes through

2859
02:03:32.600 --> 02:03:34.890
Your voice sounds like Sidhu's.

2860
02:03:34.980 --> 02:03:38.650
Yeah. everything in this world looks
or sounds like something else.

2861
02:03:38.730 --> 02:03:41.480
Like I once saw a guy on Savdhaan India
who looked just like you.

2862
02:03:41.560 --> 02:03:42.020
Really?

2863
02:03:42.100 --> 02:03:44.100
Tell me. where do I drop you guys?

2864
02:03:44.180 --> 02:03:45.800
You don't need a drop us.
you need to catch someone.

2865
02:03:45.890 --> 02:03:47.300
You need to catch that man.

2866
02:03:47.520 --> 02:03:49.400
But why do you want to catch
that harmless soul?

2867
02:03:49.480 --> 02:03:51.230
We want to catch his friend actually.

2868
02:03:51.310 --> 02:03:52.940
He changed religions
and married three times.

2869
02:03:53.020 --> 02:03:54.690
He's a scoundrel.
Please hurry.

2870
02:03:54.770 --> 02:03:56.650
Maybe he had his reasons to do it.

2871
02:03:56.730 --> 02:03:59.440
What could've made him so helpless?
If I see him. I'd shoot him.

2872
02:03:59.520 --> 02:04:00.310
No!

2873
02:04:00.390 --> 02:04:01.550
How can you just shoot him?

2874
02:04:01.640 --> 02:04:02.430
He's my son.

2875
02:04:02.520 --> 02:04:03.190
- He's my husband.
- He's my husband.

2876
02:04:03.270 --> 02:04:04.610
Then what should I do?

2877
02:04:04.640 --> 02:04:06.010
I say you should forgive him.

2878
02:04:06.100 --> 02:04:07.260
How do I forgive him?

2879
02:04:08.390 --> 02:04:10.680
It's very simple. just say
"I forgive you."

2880
02:04:11.140 --> 02:04:13.390
Every faith is this world teaches
the same truth.

2881
02:04:13.560 --> 02:04:15.060
Anyone can punish...

2882
02:04:15.230 --> 02:04:18.440
Only the divine can forgive.

2883
02:04:18.520 --> 02:04:20.480
So forgive and applaud.

2884
02:04:23.680 --> 02:04:26.760
- There he is. Follow him.
- Yes. tell me. Harbhajan?

2885
02:04:26.850 --> 02:04:31.220
Bro. your dad and Mirza chased me. now D.D.
and some Sikh gent has joined too!

2886
02:04:31.390 --> 02:04:33.470
That's your buddy.

2887
02:04:33.640 --> 02:04:34.180
Huh?

2888
02:04:34.270 --> 02:04:37.440
All his relatives have surrounded him.

2889
02:04:37.520 --> 02:04:38.480
Do one thing...

2890
02:04:38.560 --> 02:04:42.400
receive them. accept whatever gifts
they give like blessings.

2891
02:04:42.480 --> 02:04:43.310
Oh. my God!

2892
02:04:43.390 --> 02:04:46.510
- Meanwhile I'll go get married. Got it?
- What are you doing? Hurry up!

2893
02:04:46.600 --> 02:04:48.640
- Stop or I'll hit you!
- What are you saying?

2894
02:04:48.890 --> 02:04:50.180
Yes. yes. sir. catch him!

2895
02:04:50.680 --> 02:04:52.680
Taking singles won't help.

2896
02:04:52.890 --> 02:04:55.640
You'll be praised only if you smash a six.

2897
02:04:57.100 --> 02:04:58.850
Stop! Stop! Stop!

2898
02:04:59.600 --> 02:05:02.260
And the batsman's smashed
it out of the park!

2899
02:05:02.390 --> 02:05:05.260
It's airborne... going by air mail!

2900
02:05:19.020 --> 02:05:20.560
- Come on. let's catch that rascal!
- Hubby!

2901
02:05:22.600 --> 02:05:23.260
Get out of there!

2902
02:05:23.350 --> 02:05:24.890
Abba. can I come to your wedding too?

2903
02:05:24.980 --> 02:05:26.650
It'd be great if your dad
actually manages to make it.

2904
02:05:26.680 --> 02:05:27.600
Go!

2905
02:05:31.600 --> 02:05:33.220
- Tell me. where is Mehmood?!
- Don't hit me! Don't hit me!

2906
02:05:33.310 --> 02:05:34.230
Tell me where is my friend?

2907
02:05:34.310 --> 02:05:35.480
Let me take you to his wedding.

2908
02:05:35.600 --> 02:05:36.300
Please don't hit me!

2909
02:05:36.390 --> 02:05:37.470
Tell me. where is Mohan!

2910
02:05:37.560 --> 02:05:38.270
Mohan's found Saniya.

2911
02:05:38.350 --> 02:05:40.050
He's turned Sikh
and is about to marry her.

2912
02:05:42.310 --> 02:05:45.360
Friends. with your blessings.

2913
02:05:45.430 --> 02:05:49.140
the bride and groom.
after completing the engagement ceremony.

2914
02:05:49.230 --> 02:05:52.110
will head to the Gurudwara
for their wedding.

2915
02:05:53.810 --> 02:05:56.270
Thank you! Thank you! Thank you!

2916
02:05:59.390 --> 02:06:00.350
Bring it here. dear.

2917
02:06:02.430 --> 02:06:03.180
Here. dear.

2918
02:06:03.390 --> 02:06:04.260
Go on. exchange the rings.

2919
02:06:09.520 --> 02:06:11.190
Your turn. son.

2920
02:06:23.140 --> 02:06:24.180
Let's go.

2921
02:06:29.640 --> 02:06:30.390
Stop!

2922
02:06:30.480 --> 02:06:31.440
Stop!

2923
02:06:31.680 --> 02:06:33.350
- This wedding can't take place!
- This wedding can't take place!

2924
02:06:33.430 --> 02:06:35.600
- Stop it! Stop right there!
- We won't allow it! Leave!

2925
02:06:35.680 --> 02:06:37.390
- Stop this wedding!
- Stop!

2926
02:06:37.520 --> 02:06:38.810
- This wedding can't take place!
- Stop!

2927
02:06:38.890 --> 02:06:40.930
- This wedding can't take place!
- Stop!

2928
02:06:41.020 --> 02:06:42.060
We won't spare anyone!

2929
02:06:42.600 --> 02:06:43.680
Stop it!

2930
02:06:45.310 --> 02:06:46.310
Mohan!

2931
02:06:46.730 --> 02:06:47.980
Everyone. leave!

2932
02:06:48.770 --> 02:06:50.270
Stop!

2933
02:06:51.020 --> 02:06:52.650
Stop all this!

2934
02:06:52.680 --> 02:06:54.510
Mr. Registrar.
this wedding can't take place!

2935
02:06:58.060 --> 02:06:59.560
This wedding can't take place!

2936
02:06:59.600 --> 02:07:00.390
No. I won't go with you!

2937
02:07:00.480 --> 02:07:02.360
You will only marry the boy
I chose for you.

2938
02:07:06.430 --> 02:07:08.510
You're going to marry Mehmood!

2939
02:07:13.520 --> 02:07:14.690
I don't want to hear a word.

2940
02:07:14.770 --> 02:07:16.440
I'll only marry Mohan.

2941
02:07:23.020 --> 02:07:25.770
This is my last warning...
stop this wedding!

2942
02:07:25.850 --> 02:07:28.430
Who do you think you are.
trying to stop my daughter's wedding?

2943
02:07:28.770 --> 02:07:29.900
She's getting married!

2944
02:07:30.230 --> 02:07:32.270
I'll see who has the guts to stop it.

2945
02:07:33.680 --> 02:07:35.140
I can't marry him.

2946
02:07:36.680 --> 02:07:37.760
What happened. dear?

2947
02:07:37.850 --> 02:07:39.140
What are you saying. Simran?

2948
02:07:39.480 --> 02:07:41.110
I'm not Simran. I'm Saniya.

2949
02:07:41.390 --> 02:07:42.350
Saniya!

2950
02:07:42.730 --> 02:07:43.690
Saniya...

2951
02:07:44.310 --> 02:07:45.310
Yes. Saniya.

2952
02:07:46.180 --> 02:07:50.510
Mr. Manjeet. I love Mohan.
I can't marry you.

2953
02:07:50.600 --> 02:07:51.850
You can marry me.

2954
02:07:52.180 --> 02:07:53.970
Just look at me once.

2955
02:07:54.730 --> 02:07:57.360
I can't look at anyone but Mohan.

2956
02:07:57.600 --> 02:08:00.350
Saniya.
Mohan's hiding somewhere inside Manjeet.

2957
02:08:00.430 --> 02:08:01.510
Just look at me.

2958
02:08:02.680 --> 02:08:03.800
I can't.

2959
02:08:09.890 --> 02:08:11.350
Saniya. please stop!

2960
02:08:12.520 --> 02:08:15.810
I was 16 when I fell in love with you.

2961
02:08:16.390 --> 02:08:17.680
I'm 32 now.

2962
02:08:18.140 --> 02:08:20.600
I won't even be able
to have kids after I turn 65..

2963
02:08:21.390 --> 02:08:25.800
That engineer-baba was right...
one day. you'd forget me.

2964
02:08:27.770 --> 02:08:31.730
If fate doesn't approve.
then you'll forget him someday.

2965
02:08:32.390 --> 02:08:34.470
But remember what you said?

2966
02:08:36.100 --> 02:08:38.890
I'd rather die than forget him.

2967
02:08:47.770 --> 02:08:50.520
I'd rather die than forget him.

2968
02:09:10.270 --> 02:09:13.230
Saniya! You're making a huge mistake.

2969
02:09:13.480 --> 02:09:14.440
Enough. Abba!

2970
02:09:14.810 --> 02:09:15.480
Not today.

2971
02:09:15.560 --> 02:09:16.900
Your Abba's right.

2972
02:09:16.980 --> 02:09:18.900
This wretched man's already married
three women

2973
02:09:18.980 --> 02:09:20.060
and switched his faith three times.

2974
02:09:20.140 --> 02:09:21.600
Mohan would never do that!

2975
02:09:21.640 --> 02:09:22.600
That's exactly what he did.

2976
02:09:22.680 --> 02:09:24.010
Here's the proof...

2977
02:09:24.310 --> 02:09:25.110
Jenny.

2978
02:09:25.600 --> 02:09:26.470
Meera.

2979
02:09:26.560 --> 02:09:27.610
And Ruhi!

2980
02:09:27.640 --> 02:09:29.970
And today. as a Sikh. he was getting
married for the fourth time... with you.

2981
02:09:31.640 --> 02:09:33.600
Mohan. is that true?

2982
02:09:37.770 --> 02:09:39.150
Yes. Saniya. it's true.

2983
02:09:40.730 --> 02:09:42.060
They're all my wives.

2984
02:09:52.060 --> 02:09:53.310
You deceived us.

2985
02:09:54.600 --> 02:09:55.760
You deceived them.

2986
02:09:57.230 --> 02:09:58.310
You lied to them.

2987
02:09:59.350 --> 02:10:00.890
Is that what we taught you?

2988
02:10:02.930 --> 02:10:04.510
Is this why I brought you into this world?

2989
02:10:05.230 --> 02:10:10.230
Not just gave you life.
we gave you a family. culture. and faith.

2990
02:10:10.520 --> 02:10:12.400
and you went around changing
your religion?

2991
02:10:12.640 --> 02:10:16.470
I didn't change it. I embraced them all.

2992
02:10:16.640 --> 02:10:20.220
You think you're the constitution
of India to embrace them all?

2993
02:10:20.390 --> 02:10:21.470
No. Father.

2994
02:10:22.100 --> 02:10:23.430
I'm just an ordinary man.

2995
02:10:23.640 --> 02:10:28.220
I don't know religion in depth.
but all of you do.

2996
02:10:28.600 --> 02:10:30.260
For you. your religion is the greatest.

2997
02:10:30.480 --> 02:10:31.810
For Mr. Mirza. his is.

2998
02:10:31.980 --> 02:10:33.400
For Mr. David. his is.

2999
02:10:34.640 --> 02:10:38.970
If every faith is good.
then what's so wrong in embracing them all?

3000
02:10:39.850 --> 02:10:45.390
Or is my fault that
I can't find fault in any?

3001
02:10:47.020 --> 02:10:50.770
And about those three marriages.
about deceiving these girls...

3002
02:10:51.060 --> 02:10:53.520
I never lied to anyone. Saniya.

3003
02:10:54.390 --> 02:10:57.300
Every time I tried to marry you.
I ended up marrying someone else instead.

3004
02:10:58.310 --> 02:11:00.310
For you. I became Mehmood from Mohan.

3005
02:11:00.850 --> 02:11:02.100
Michael from Mehmood.

3006
02:11:02.730 --> 02:11:05.310
and today. Manjeet from Michael.

3007
02:11:06.730 --> 02:11:07.690
Hey! Hey! Hey!

3008
02:11:07.770 --> 02:11:08.690
Brother!

3009
02:11:09.680 --> 02:11:10.470
- Mohan!
- Hey!

3010
02:11:10.560 --> 02:11:11.860
What was their fault?

3011
02:11:11.980 --> 02:11:14.610
Who gave you the right
to wreck their lives?

3012
02:11:14.930 --> 02:11:15.970
Mohan!

3013
02:11:16.060 --> 02:11:17.020
What are you doing?

3014
02:11:17.100 --> 02:11:18.800
- Mohan!
- You could've just refused to marry them!

3015
02:11:18.890 --> 02:11:19.640
Stop it!

3016
02:11:26.350 --> 02:11:29.640
He told each one of them
he couldn't marry them...

3017
02:11:30.600 --> 02:11:31.930
but every time. they said the same thing.

3018
02:11:32.640 --> 02:11:35.390
"If you call off the wedding.
I'll end my life."

3019
02:11:35.810 --> 02:11:36.650
So what was he supposed to do?

3020
02:11:36.730 --> 02:11:38.230
Should he have let them die?

3021
02:11:38.390 --> 02:11:42.470
He sacrificed his own love just
to save their lives.

3022
02:11:42.890 --> 02:11:45.720
He could've easily walked away.

3023
02:11:46.560 --> 02:11:47.520
but he didn't

3024
02:11:48.680 --> 02:11:52.850
because he knew Jenny struggles
to breathe.

3025
02:11:53.890 --> 02:11:56.050
Ruhi has her parents
and a child depending on her.

3026
02:11:57.060 --> 02:12:00.480
and his own parents had promised
to keep Meera happy.

3027
02:12:01.980 --> 02:12:04.980
For someone's life. for someone's promise
and for someone's bond's sake...

3028
02:12:05.230 --> 02:12:06.940
He tried to fulfil
all his responsibilities.

3029
02:12:07.730 --> 02:12:09.650
He tried to keep everyone happy.

3030
02:12:10.350 --> 02:12:11.850
Now you decide...

3031
02:12:12.600 --> 02:12:14.470
a man who's lived for everyone else...

3032
02:12:14.770 --> 02:12:18.480
does he deserve punishment.
or does he deserve to be with his love today?

3033
02:12:26.850 --> 02:12:28.720
I cannot punish him.

3034
02:12:30.600 --> 02:12:33.510
When my boyfriend left me to die.

3035
02:12:35.270 --> 02:12:36.980
he was the one who saved my life.

3036
02:12:38.560 --> 02:12:39.980
I can't hate you.

3037
02:12:41.350 --> 02:12:42.760
I love you. Michael.

3038
02:12:45.270 --> 02:12:46.610
What can I even say?

3039
02:12:47.770 --> 02:12:51.520
He married me to keep my father's word...

3040
02:12:53.520 --> 02:12:55.900
so how could he break
his promise to Saniya?

3041
02:12:58.020 --> 02:12:59.480
I've got no complaints against you.

3042
02:13:02.180 --> 02:13:03.390
I love you. Mohan.

3043
02:13:05.850 --> 02:13:08.510
I've got no complaints
against Mehmood either.

3044
02:13:08.770 --> 02:13:10.560
He's the one who was wronged.

3045
02:13:11.600 --> 02:13:14.300
I'd already been divorced twice.

3046
02:13:15.600 --> 02:13:19.640
He could've walked away too.
but he didn't.

3047
02:13:21.060 --> 02:13:22.400
I love you. Mehmood.

3048
02:13:23.310 --> 02:13:24.440
I love you.

3049
02:13:27.600 --> 02:13:29.550
Saniya. what do you say?

3050
02:13:33.520 --> 02:13:35.810
You shouldn't have been this good.
Mohan...

3051
02:13:36.560 --> 02:13:38.520
now everyone's fallen in love with you.

3052
02:13:52.560 --> 02:13:55.650
There you go. I guess
all the garland were always meant for him.

3053
02:13:55.770 --> 02:13:56.690
Wait a minute...

3054
02:13:58.600 --> 02:13:59.680
Surleen. you?

3055
02:14:01.480 --> 02:14:04.270
There's a garland for you too. Mr. Hubby.

3056
02:14:09.770 --> 02:14:11.730
Your brother's finally settling down
as well today.

3057
02:14:15.180 --> 02:14:16.390
Hey! Hey! Hey! What--

3058
02:14:16.480 --> 02:14:17.520
- Mohan!
- Mohan!

3059
02:14:17.600 --> 02:14:18.760
- Mohan!
- Mohan!

3060
02:14:19.430 --> 02:14:20.640
- Mohan!
- Mohan!

3061
02:14:20.730 --> 02:14:21.860
- Mohan!
- Mohan!

3062
02:14:22.640 --> 02:14:23.680
Ambulance!

3063
02:14:29.100 --> 02:14:30.600
Are you okay? How are you feeling now?

3064
02:14:31.890 --> 02:14:32.890
- Here. eat this.
- Feeling better now?

3065
02:14:32.980 --> 02:14:34.980
Mom. you're happy
with my four marriages. right?

3066
02:14:35.730 --> 02:14:36.770
Not four. son... five.

3067
02:14:36.850 --> 02:14:37.600
Five?!

3068
02:14:37.680 --> 02:14:39.350
Mom. you're just panicking
and can't count straight.

3069
02:14:39.520 --> 02:14:41.770
No. really... not four. five wives.

3070
02:14:41.850 --> 02:14:43.680
There is no power
and no strength except with Allah!

3071
02:14:44.390 --> 02:14:45.300
Five? How?

3072
02:14:45.850 --> 02:14:47.050
When you were born.

3073
02:14:47.140 --> 02:14:50.140
the astrologer said
you'd never find happiness in marriage.

3074
02:14:50.430 --> 02:14:52.890
He was right... four marriages done.
and still no peace.

3075
02:14:52.980 --> 02:14:55.020
But we thought you'd never
get married at all.

3076
02:14:55.100 --> 02:14:58.010
so I promised your hand to my friend's
daughter the day you were born.

3077
02:14:58.100 --> 02:14:58.850
What?!

3078
02:14:58.930 --> 02:15:03.430
And your father had already
promised you to Meera's father.

3079
02:15:04.310 --> 02:15:07.230
Why did you two have
to test every experiment on me!

3080
02:15:07.350 --> 02:15:08.510
Hang on a second.

3081
02:15:08.600 --> 02:15:10.300
If I'd only married once.
it would've been fine...

